fields.article_title: Earthquake loss estimation for Europe's historic town centres.
fields.name: D'Ayala etal (1997) - MUR+STDRE (PGA)
fields.general_comments: Sample Data: The case study consisted of 8 urban blocks, about 200 residential buildings in the Alfama district in Lisbon, chosen to be representative of the building stock (between 2 and 6 storeys).
fields.authors: D. DAyala, R. Spence, C. Oliveira  A. Pomonis.
